            "value" : "Next Week's Goal"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "毎週日曜日は、weekで一週間を振り返る日。\n良かったこと、次週への改善策などを\nゆっくり整理し、自分の成長を確認しましょう。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Every Sunday is the day to reflect on the week with week.\nTake your time to organize what went well,\nimprovements for next week, and confirm your growth."
          }
        }
      }
    },
